Title: An Act Changing the Name of Ubol Elementary School in the Municipality of Simunul, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Datu Amilbangsa Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 329
An Act Changing the Name of Ubol Elementary School in the Municipality of Simunul, Province of Tawi-Tawi, to Datu Amilbangsa Elementary School
Section 1. The name of Ubol Elementary School in the Municipality of Simunul, Province of Tawi-Tawi, is changed to Datu Amilbangsa Elementary School.1awp++i1
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.
Approved: January 19, 1983
